  "3256150": {
    "name": "姆明：暖心冬日",
    "steam_appid": 3256150,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>继《<strong>史力奇奇遇记：姆明山谷之歌</strong>》之后，其创作团队再度从托芙·杨松备受珍爱的姆明故事中汲取灵感，献上一段暖彻心扉的全新冒险。这一次，你将陪伴姆明，踏上一段清冷而又迷人的冬日之旅。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/595c9e99acffb7cb82e161b1a3eb228a.poster.avif?t=1771943963\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/595c9e99acffb7cb82e161b1a3eb228a.webm?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/595c9e99acffb7cb82e161b1a3eb228a.mp4?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>当姆明从冬眠中意外惊醒，他平生第一次发现自己孤身一人，置身于一片几乎认不出的陌生天地。冰雪女王为姆明谷熟悉的风光，披上了一层冰霜织成的面纱。起初，小小的姆明只是想找个伴儿，好驱散这恼人的冬天。但他却终究不情不愿地踏上了一场走向未知的旅程。他将在这趟旅程中学会结交新朋友，并向那些比自己更需要温暖的生灵伸出援手。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/e7721c48f6441ff09531f7cc87b3b26a.poster.avif?t=1771943963\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/e7721c48f6441ff09531f7cc87b3b26a.webm?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/e7721c48f6441ff09531f7cc87b3b26a.mp4?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索冬日奇幻仙境。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >徜徉于汲取了北欧自然灵韵的壮美风光，探访姆明谷及其周边的巍峨群山与静谧森林。结识新朋，并透过姆明的双眼，去体验这生平第一个冬季。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/a56a237fdf937f8b51090db0986438bf.poster.avif?t=1771943963\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/a56a237fdf937f8b51090db0986438bf.webm?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/a56a237fdf937f8b51090db0986438bf.mp4?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与精心构筑的温馨场景互动，沉浸其中。 </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冬日固然严酷，却也藏着无尽妙趣！邂逅姆明的旧雨新知，在解开谜题与完成探险的途中，向他们伸出援手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/9efb428325d121374b774e65bc3f2bad.poster.avif?t=1771943963\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/9efb428325d121374b774e65bc3f2bad.webm?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/9efb428325d121374b774e65bc3f2bad.mp4?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>帮助姆明直面内心的恐惧。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对姆明而言，这个寒冷的季节里，满是挑战与未知。尽管前路偶有惊惧与艰辛，但在邻里间的羁绊与善意中，亦藏着暖意等待你去发掘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/9bf38ac5b0d5a233606f389fd26aac14.poster.avif?t=1771943963\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/9bf38ac5b0d5a233606f389fd26aac14.webm?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/9bf38ac5b0d5a233606f389fd26aac14.mp4?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>重现托芙·杨松的经典《姆明谷的冬天》。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于姆明的粉丝，这是一次充满情怀的回望；而对于初涉这个奇妙世界的新手，这亦是一个亲切的起点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/b06b885b3508fdaff269ec24ca348349.poster.avif?t=1771943963\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/b06b885b3508fdaff269ec24ca348349.webm?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/b06b885b3508fdaff269ec24ca348349.mp4?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《史力奇奇遇记：姆明山谷之歌》的精神续作。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>《姆明：暖心冬日》是一部以故事驱动的温馨解谜冒险之旅。它将透过屡获殊荣的独立工作室 Hyper Games 的奇思妙想，邀你重返那个如诗如画的姆明谷。本作并非《史力奇奇遇记：姆明山谷之歌》的直接续篇，但在精神气质与诸多设计上，都可谓一脉相承。两款作品皆可独立品味，游玩顺序亦无先后之分。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/f73ce2359f74edbb3cee7bcd1a908c6f.poster.avif?t=1771943963\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/f73ce2359f74edbb3cee7bcd1a908c6f.webm?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/f73ce2359f74edbb3cee7bcd1a908c6f.mp4?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作将于 2026 年面世，即刻在 Steam 添加心愿单，或在我们的网站订阅新闻邮件，获取更多资讯！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/cf399cb558143cea4b8f823de50e0f09.poster.avif?t=1771943963\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/cf399cb558143cea4b8f823de50e0f09.webm?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256150/extras/cf399cb558143cea4b8f823de50e0f09.mp4?t=1771943963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
